    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper and tear into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop <strong>half</strong> the <strong>basil </strong>finely, including the stalks (reserve the rest for later!)</p>",
