    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, remove the <strong>bay leaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves] </span></strong>from the tomato sauce and top with the <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>and <strong>reserved basil leaves</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>stove-top aubergine parmigiana</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> with the <strong>crispy breadcrumbs </strong>– these are your <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
